http://screenshotcomparison.com/comparison/13509&lt;/a&gt;

So what you see is what you get, you loose a bit brightness but gain a clearer picture and quality.

For the Audio, well cleaned it up too, removed noise,hiss,hum and some scratches, cant do anything about the slight metallic voices here and there. all in all watchable

